OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F437A1783718417
OL,3,CParents call for better allergy
OL,4,Cprotection in schools after son's death
OL,6,FThe parents of a five-year-old boy who
OL,7,Fdied after suffering an allergic
OL,8,Freaction at school are calling on the
OL,9,FWelsh Government to introduce
OL,10,FBenedict's Law in Wales.
OL,12,FHelen and Nick Blythe have campaigned
OL,13,Ffor the changes since their son
OL,14,FBenedict died after suffering an
OL,15,Fanaphylactic reaction at school in
OL,16,FLincolnshire in December 2021.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G1/11
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,438,430,260,120,000,100
PN,43702
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F437A1783718417
OL,3,CParents call for better allergy
OL,4,Cprotection in schools after son's death
OL,6,FThe couple say the campaign is driven
OL,7,Fby Benedict's memory and by a
OL,8,Fdetermination to prevent other
OL,9,Ffamilies from experiencing what they
OL,10,Fwent through.
OL,12,FNow they are urging the Welsh
OL,13,FGovernment to introduce protections
OL,14,Fthat are due to be rolled out in
OL,15,Fschools across England from September.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G2/11
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,438,430,260,120,000,100
PN,43703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F437A1783718417
OL,3,CParents call for better allergy
OL,4,Cprotection in schools after son's death
OL,6,FThe guidance sets out expectations for
OL,7,Fschools to have an allergy policy,
OL,8,Ftrain staff to recognise and respond
OL,9,Fto allergic reactions, stock spare
OL,10,Fadrenaline auto-injectors (AAIs), and
OL,11,Fprovide individual healthcare plans
OL,12,Ffor children whose allergies require
OL,13,Fmanagement at school. Primary
OL,14,Flegislation is due to come into force
OL,15,Fin England in 2027.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G3/11
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,438,430,260,120,000,100
PN,43704
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F437A1783718417
OL,3,CParents call for better allergy
OL,4,Cprotection in schools after son's death
OL,6,FHelen Blythe said: "Every child
OL,7,Fdeserves to be safe at school,
OL,8,Fregardless of which side of the border
OL,9,Fthey live on. Welsh families should
OL,10,Fnot have to wait years for protections
OL,11,Fthat have already been recognised as
OL,12,Fnecessary elsewhere."
OL,14,FShe added: "Wales has an opportunity
OL,15,Fto build on that work rather than
OL,16,Fstarting again.
OL,18,F"We are asking the Welsh Government to
OL,19,Fcommit to adopting Benedict's Law so
OL,20,Fthat every school has the same minimum
OL,21,Fstandards for allergy safety.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G4/11
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,438,430,260,120,000,100
PN,43705
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F437A1783718417
OL,3,CParents call for better allergy
OL,4,Cprotection in schools after son's death
OL,6,F"It's simply not fair that children
OL,7,Fwith allergies in Wales should return
OL,8,Fto school in the autumn without the
OL,9,Fsame protections as those in England
OL,10,Fwill receive from Benedict's Law."
OL,12,FAt St Michael's Catholic Primary
OL,13,FSchool in Treforest, pupils Evie and
OL,14,FJayden are already familiar with
OL,15,Fmanaging their allergies.
OL,17,FEvie said: "These are my two epipens,
OL,18,Fand all this comes home with me and I
OL,19,Ftake it everywhere I go and these two
OL,20,Fstay in school."
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G5/11
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,438,430,260,120,000,100
PN,43706
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F437A1783718417
OL,3,CParents call for better allergy
OL,4,Cprotection in schools after son's death
OL,6,FJayden said: "I just mainly try to
OL,7,Favoid foods that have my allergies in,
OL,8,Fand that's about all."
OL,10,FHe said his friends also help him
OL,11,Fmanage his allergies.
OL,13,F"Yeah and they try to check the
OL,14,Fingredients in the foods that they
OL,15,Fwant to give me if I want to try some."
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G6/11
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
