PN,43707
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F437A1783718417
OL,3,CParents call for better allergy
OL,4,Cprotection in schools after son's death
OL,6,FHeadteacher Joanna Taylor has
OL,7,Fintroduced additional allergy safety
OL,8,Fmeasures at the school, including
OL,9,Fstaff training, self-funded spare
OL,10,Fepipens, allergy awareness lessons and
OL,11,Fa nut-free packed lunch policy.
OL,13,FShowing the school's first aid and
OL,14,Fsafeguarding area, she said: "So this
OL,15,Fis our first aid/safeguarding area. As
OL,16,Fyou can see we've got both epipens
OL,17,Fhere ready to be able to be used. They
OL,18,Fare to be used only once we've called
OL,19,F999 and have instructions. All my
OL,20,Fstaff are trained on how to use the
OL,21,Fepipen."
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G7/11
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,438,430,260,120,000,100
PN,43708
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F437A1783718417
OL,3,CParents call for better allergy
OL,4,Cprotection in schools after son's death
OL,6,FSchools in Wales are not legally
OL,7,Frequired to stock spare adrenaline
OL,8,Fauto-injectors.
OL,10,FJoanna added: "There are so many
OL,11,Fallergies that children and adults can
OL,12,Fsuffer from today, so just educating
OL,13,Feveryone helps doesn't it? And that
OL,14,Fpeace of mind is priceless."
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G8/11
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,438,430,260,120,000,100
PN,43709
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F437A1783718417
OL,3,CParents call for better allergy
OL,4,Cprotection in schools after son's death
OL,6,FThe Benedict Blythe Foundation is
OL,7,Fcalling on the Welsh Government to
OL,8,Fpublish an updated timetable for its
OL,9,Freview of allergy guidance, commit to
OL,10,Fintroducing equivalent protections for
OL,11,Fchildren in Wales, and work with
OL,12,Ffamilies, clinicians and education
OL,13,Fleaders to implement a Welsh version
OL,14,Fof Benedict's Law.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G9/11
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,438,430,260,120,000,100
PN,43710
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F437A1783718417
OL,3,CParents call for better allergy
OL,4,Cprotection in schools after son's death
OL,6,FA Welsh Government spokesperson said:
OL,7,F"It is important that learners living
OL,8,Fwith allergies are supported. All
OL,9,FSchools are already subject to legal
OL,10,Frequirements and have been issued with
OL,11,Fstatutory guidance, which covers
OL,12,Frecord keeping, storage and
OL,13,Fadministration of medicines, emergency
OL,14,Fprocedures and staff training
OL,15,Frequirements to support children and
OL,16,Fyoung people with healthcare needs,
OL,17,Fincluding allergies.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                  G10/11
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,438,430,260,120,000,100
PN,43711
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F437A1783718417
OL,3,CParents call for better allergy
OL,4,Cprotection in schools after son's death
OL,6,F"We are currently reviewing the
OL,7,Fexisting statutory guidance and will
OL,8,Fconsider Benedict's Law, to inform
OL,9,Ffuture policy in Wales."
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                  G11/11
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
